Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the Federation Forces have exhausted{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, they lack the strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result, they'll probably\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the sort of thing Revil would plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the more reason why\Nwe must try to avoid further warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what the Solar Ray Is for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll wipe out the Federation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can do it... Right, Garma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking to defuse a situation that was\Nno longer under his control...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sovereign Degwin departed\Nfrom the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander Gihren Zabi,\Nof course, had not been informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A Cosmic Glow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown old, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Call from Captain Asakura,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reporting, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Solar Ray is now operational.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll reach critical point in two hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had to use the critically permeable{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that were created for testing purposes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result, the Solar Ray system{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are its capabilities as we predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A 3-second continuous irradiation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and an angle adjustment of{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am impressed.\NThe preparations must be flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs to the Gelgoog should be finished\Nwithin 20 to 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that's done,\Nwe'll commence our second wave of attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After we defeat the Trojan Horse's group,\Nwe'll head immediately for A Baoa Qu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our intelligence indicates that Revil's\Nmain fleet will ignore Granada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, there's something\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you abandon your plans\Nto overthrow the Zabi family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My... plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent some time playing with young Casval\Nwhen he was about four years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you summoned me,\NLady Kycilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...I knew that a time like this would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't make it any less frightening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand won't stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the same way...\Nwhen I found out about your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You had sent Lalah to the Flanagan Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that you had\Nalmost clairvoyant insight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I ordered a thorough investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah made you believe\Nin the existence of Newtypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you now have greater goals\Nthan overthrowing the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gihren has taken command\Nat A Baoa Qu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything else will be dealt with\Nafter we defeat the Federation. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtypes, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're different from espers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging from what Amuro said,\Nthe enemy must have superhuman abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's assume so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can possibly fight\Nagainst an enemy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Amuro,\Nbut if that Tricorn Hat appears again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll take care of it...\NAt this point, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Right now, you're exhibiting\NNewtype potential, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only logical explanation\Nfor everything that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I am a Newtype,\NI'm not special!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With the way we've been fighting, I think\Nall the White Base crew must be Newtypes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we couldn't have made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have a point there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still sense something\Nextraordinary about you, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been especially convinced\Nsince encountering that Tricorn Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And... that "la... la" sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! We're in diamond formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Now hurry up and send out\Nall the mobile suit teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stage an all-out assault on the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal is to sink at least half the vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you'll deal with the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head out in the Gelgoog, but this time\NI'll be following your orders, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've surpassed me now, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I want you to wear\Nyour normal suit whenever you sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suit launching complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Assault formation assumed\Nwith Captain Char's Zanzibar in the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hold here in the Gwazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds after Captain Char launches,\Ngive him 30 seconds of covering fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy vessels are on the move!\NThey're passing the F-line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai! Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about shifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave things in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtypes, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! Make sure they launch quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Something wrong?\N- N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they'll be okay! We'd better have\Na place to return to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,10 degrees starboard, at 1:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna change their course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Four ships coming up portside!\N- Put up a barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Two vessels down on each side!\NThe enemy's started evasive action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Anti-air fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll send in the mobile suits next!\NHere they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in teams of 5 or 6. I see at least 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the Tricorn Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! The control...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,La... la...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A... mu... ro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting, Lalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'll hurt Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bad person, trying to harm Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength you're displaying tells me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I don't defeat you, Char will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Char?! ...- So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you arrived too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why did you have to appear now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you keep fighting like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no one to defend\Nand nothing to protect, and yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's no family in your heart.\NAnd no homeland either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it wrong of me to fight\Nif I have nothing to defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you doing, Lalah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting for the one person\Nwho saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... There's nothing else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It's a truth that one lives for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean nothing that we met?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, was this destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I believe so.\NI think this was destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is fate... then life is just too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah, open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Could you really be right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fate, as you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why now?!\NWhy now, of all times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're all burdened\Nwith our own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah! Stop fooling around with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Char...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother! Please pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous! Stay back, Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, it's me! Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah! I need to crush that Gundam!\NGive your guidance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you take Lalah away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, you're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Artesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,LALAH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,People are changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're becoming like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right about that, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do you honestly believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I were able\Nto understand each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One day people will even\Nbe able to control time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see time itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,tsubasa wo hirogete anata wo dakuwa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,ashita anata wa sabishii kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sonna koto nai watashitachi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,dakara ne oyasumi Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,konna futari ga sudatsu tomo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,tada kanashimi ga hatenakute hatenakute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,akogareru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yume sore wa yume yume
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ashita futari wa chimidoro de
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,kaze ni kaze ni kaze ni mau
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spread my wings and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you'll be lonely tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not feel such things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So please sleep now, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of us should leave the nest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The sadness is endless, endless
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We yearn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream, it is a dream, a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we will both be bloodsoaked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dancing in the wind, the wind, the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,La... Lalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done something terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done something I can never take\Nback!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Zanzibar!\NConcentrate all fire on the Zanzibar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get the Trojan Horse! Just that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Gwazine is our only remaining ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- How pathetic.\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam pilot's Newtype abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...are becoming even greater.\NIt's overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Kycilia, we've received orders from\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Federation's main fleet\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Zeon fleets In the Solar Ray's firing path{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The operation will commence at 21:05.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me...\NThey're using the Solar Ray in 30 minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Solar Ray?\NThey're going to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too rash...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Gihren plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late to the rendezvous\Nwith the main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. Can the Salamis behind us keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it. Let's go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no more Zeons in this airspace,\Nso they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Newtype that challenged Amuro\Nis no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I can still fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Haro? I'm doing fine, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, brainwave level excellent!\NExcellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Federation fleet,\Nled by General Revil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...was gathering at the third battle line\Nleading to A Baoa Qu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at this point that General Revil\Nannounced their target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They were to fight past A Baoa Qu,\Nand invade the Zeon homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Degwin has arrived\Nfor peace negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Gihren speaking from A Baoa Qu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now announce the final target\Nof the Solar Ray system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The main forces of the enemy's Revil Fleet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...are split into three groups.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if we aim the Solar Ray at Gel Dorva...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we should be able to take out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Solar Ray system...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...stand by! sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar Ray system, stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Generator systems: no problems!\NMicrowave transmitters: operational!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Output: 8500 gigawatts per hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust firing angle... down 012, right 0032!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Primary target is Gel Dorva!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Musai over generator system 825! Clear out!\NYour shadow will lower our output!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't do it! Don't move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People are melting in a whirlpool of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the light of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the rivalry between Gihren and Kycilia\Ndrive Zeon into a crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The surviving members of the Earth\NFederation Forces stage their final assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Char, too, makes a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Amuro almost seems\Nto follow Lalah's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NSpace Fortress: A Baoa Qu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Space Fortress: A Baoa Qu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:24:00.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:10.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:15.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.81,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:25.19,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:29.78,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:40.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:24:00.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:10.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:15.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:25.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:29.78,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:40.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
